title C3 – Manage Vessel Types (Process View / System Sequence Diagram)
hide footbox

actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer
participant "VesselTypeController\n(API Layer)" as Controller
participant "VesselTypeMapper\n(Conversão DTO ↔ Entidade)" as Mapper
participant "PortContext\n(Entity Framework Core)" as Context
database "Database System\n(SQL / InMemory)" as DB


